OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMainly fine with some sunny
OL,6,Fspells, although these may be on the
OL,7,Fhazy side under periodic higher cloud.
OL,8,FBecoming very warm and feeling humid,
OL,9,Fwith light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FMainly fine during the
OL,12,Fevening, but becoming rather cloudy
OL,13,Ffrom the west, with a little rain
OL,14,Fspreading eastwards. Staying warm,
OL,15,Fwith light winds.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FBrightest in the southeast,
OL,18,Fwith the greatest chance of some sunny
OL,19,Fspells here. Cloudier elsewhere, with
OL,20,Fperiods of mostly light rain, easing
OL,21,Flater. Generally warm and rather humid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
